Bureau Chief Benin – A Benin based group, with the name, Aviary Club of Nigeria, (ACN), has called on all aggrieved members of the ruling All Progressives Congress in the state to sheath their sword for the interests of the people of the state.
The group also commended the Secretary to Edo State Government (SSG), Barrister Osarodion Ogie for assisting the state government in spreading even development across the state sspecially in Ikpoba-Okha Local Government Area of the state.
Speaking to newsmen in Benin City, the state coordinator of the group, Comrade Noah Idemudia said, with the level of completed and ongiong projects across the local government and the state, Barrister Osarodion Ogie has proven undenting qualities.
Idemudia expressed total confidence on his leadership to continue to deliver on the dividends of democracy to the people, while calling on pocket of individuals clamouring for his removal to abstain from such actions.
He warned against possible action-line that could steer distractions.
“Barrister Osarodion is an enigma of development in Ikpoba okha. His records are unbeatable.
“Looking at his commitments toward the grassroots in the local government, you will agree with my position on his laudable achievement thus far, across the state. We would continue to give him the necessary support as a group to do more,”he stated.